 hierarchical architecture as well as pretraining techniques.\nCandidate Topics: transformer, natural language processing, artificial intelligence, visualization, block, machine learning, text mining, deep learning, information retrieval, parsing, table, document layout analysis, natural language, feature extraction, block, task, artificial neural network, visual reasoning, image, question answering, scripting language, human computer interaction, information extraction, image retrieval, ranking, inference, text processing, sentence, data mining, multimedia, probabilistic logic, computer vision, block, pattern recognition, rule based system, usability, phrase structure rules, ranking, graphical model, natural language understanding, phrase, language model, tree, robustness, expert system, heuristics, knowledge extraction, speech recognition, automatic summarization, boosting, dialog box, relationship extraction, generative grammar, diagram, key, contrast, image processing, search engine indexing, layer, document engineering, decomposition, grammar induction, decoding methods, document retrieval, search engine, image segmentation, nesting, process, contextual image classification, sentence extraction, visual search, information visualization, encoding, layout engine, embedding, pattern recognition, modular design, tree structure, rank, recurrent neural network, thesaurus, hidden markov model, document structure description, row, reverse engineering, syntax, metrical task system, page table, unsupervised learning, computational linguistics, paragraph, font, software engineering, electronic design automation, document processing, tabnabbing, convolutional neural network, categorization, tree traversal, supervised learning'}], 'stream': False, 'seed': 347} failed after all attempts. Saving errors: [{'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}}, {'error': {'mes