ate Topics: landmark, orientation, artificial intelligence, face, modality, feature, representation, machine learning, facial recognition system, feature extraction, feature, computer vision, three dimensional face recognition, pattern recognition, feature learning, robustness, landmark point, artificial neural network, task, visualization, edge, state, property, representation, key, leverage, pose, exploit, rotation, image, data mining, machine vision, pattern recognition, simultaneous localization and mapping, network architecture, algorithm, process, dependency, deep learning, orthogonality, graph, routing, domain knowledge, dual, 3d reconstruction, grafting, facial expression, operator, categorization, face detection, gesture, object, service, matching, schedule, scalability, cognitive neuroscience of visual object recognition, contextual image classification, iterative reconstruction, solid modeling, robot, domain, wavelet, observer, perspective, adaptation, principal, theoretical computer science, outlier, block, variety, mnist database, 3d single object recognition, data modeling, contrast, node, image registration, rotational invariance, vertex, skeleton, face hallucination, arbiter, boosting, computational geometry, initialization, decomposition, invariant, computer graphics, component, embedding, knowledge engineering, subspace topology, stability, gradient descent, feature recognition, unsupervised learning, event, stereopsis, network topology, projection'}], 'stream': False, 'seed': 347} failed after all attempts. Saving errors: [{'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}}, {'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}}, {'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budge