tensive results verify the promising applications of our proposed approach for compact low-end cameras.\nCandidate Topics: deconvolution, artificial intelligence, algorithm, iterative reconstruction, prior probability, computer vision, image, computational photography, set, artificial neural network, convolution, deep learning, kernel, image restoration, blind deconvolution, optics algorithm, image processing, pattern recognition, convolutional neural network, computation, filter, richardson lucy deconvolution, bayesian probability, initialization, iterative method, deblurring, distortion, curve fitting, calibration, scheme, visualization, wiener deconvolution, solid modeling, algorithm design, point spread function, complement, backpropagation, set function, computational science, tracing, computer graphics images, image segmentation, kernel, library science, reconstruction algorithm, interpolation, code, feature extraction, image resolution, hash function, normalization, face, robustness, tracking, normalization, computer engineering, distortion, process, signal, posterior probability, key, mechanism, filter, pixel, frame, pattern recognition, machine learning, preprocessor, bayesian optimization, inference, sharpening, projection, field, 3d reconstruction, medical imaging, conjugate prior, estimation theory, motion blur, gamma correction, identification, feature, regularization, software, fast fourier transform, belief propagation, toolbox, kernel, eye tracking, digital image, afterimage, signal reconstruction, theoretical computer science, bayesian inference, histogram, shell, nonlinear distortion, pipeline, end to end principle, light field, iterative refinement'}], 'stream': False, 'seed': 347} failed after all attempts. Saving errors: [{'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}}, {'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423