cy.\nCandidate Topics: pixel, process, convolutional neural network, artificial intelligence, decoding methods, reduction, artificial neural network, pattern recognition, jpeg, transform coding, computer engineering, deep learning, discrete cosine transform, data compression, contextual image classification, computer vision, feature extraction, machine learning, compression, image, jpeg 2000, convolutional code, algorithm, rgb color model, computation, image compression, dimensionality reduction, quantization, image resolution, convolution, translation, time complexity, discriminative model, column, encoder, detector, representation, segmentation, data compression ratio, interpretability, quantization, code, layer, image processing, encoding, data mining, memory footprint, computational complexity theory, unsupervised learning, block, noise reduction, lossless compression, mobile device, image segmentation, liquid crystal display, projection, 2d to 3d conversion, visualization, algorithm design, wavelet transform, extract transform load, computational photography, codec, webp, entropy, feature, robustness, component, row and column spaces, scalability, theoretical computer science, decomposition, iterative reconstruction, parsing, feature learning, key, kernel, pruning, wearable computer, neural coding, inference, pipeline, normalization, object detection, dual, scheme, byte, effective method, server, compressed sensing, lapped transform, histogram, dependency, real time computing, integer programming, whitespace, hidden markov model, image restoration, classifier, graphical model'}], 'stream': False, 'seed': 347} failed after all attempts. Saving errors: [{'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}}, {'error': {'message': 'Budget has been exceeded! Current cost: 5.423352675000006, Max budget: 5.0', 'type': 'budget_exceeded', 'param': None, 'code': '400'}